Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來總算得到禁術了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 螢 很壯觀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是禁術的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我共同完成的藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:00:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.27,0:01:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把詩形大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可讓人頭痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容器可不需要感情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 再來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是土蜘蛛的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那些煩人的傢伙全都燒光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木遁之術
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你們最後不得不打倒村民了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可不在乎他們會如何哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.90,0:02:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後一招了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸 行 無 常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弁天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 你們會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四人的聯合忍術雖然很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就剩下兩人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能贏我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個禁術來控制小國
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借此動搖五大國
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能讓你得手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩形 現在可不是你休息的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須奪回螢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知死活的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想再接一次禁術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字縛之術.爆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩形 你趁機去救螢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得美 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字縛之術.炎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 這就完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就不能結印了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要加倍還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還想讓禁術…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手被封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道 或許是自然能量吸收得太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快將它停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個狀態怎麼可能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字縛之術不管用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比剛才還厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣繼續吸收自然查克拉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終會把村子一起炸飛的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土蜘蛛一族的復興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,役之行者的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於大人們一廂情願的壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢看來也承受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不懂螢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直獨自保護禁術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了一族的復興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微笑著獻出了自己的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自承受了這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 跟詩形邂逅之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然被騙了 不過遇到你這個師兄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢終於有了同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於擁有了羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一切都讓你摧毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼同伴 羈絆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這種天真的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟螢的遭遇一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了禁術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是弟子還是兒子都可以犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是忍者的生存之道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我體驗過太多 已經厭倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才先下手為強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了曾是我的師父的老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了奪取禁術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:09:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倆做的事一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父無論何時都會為弟子著想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在為我著想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論離得多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份心願都能讓人感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時 都在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢也一定感覺到了爺爺 遁兵衛 還有詩形
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的想法 肯定已經傳遞給她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定就在她的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她仍然在尋求和同伴 師父的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個一無所知的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許說這種自以為是的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就吼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字縛之術.割
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在容器失控前暫且撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把白浪帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是螢的師父
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就待在她的身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:11:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢也一定感覺到了爺爺 遁兵衛 還有詩形
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的想法 肯定已經傳遞給她了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的想法 在她的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憤怒沖昏了我的頭腦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父的想法 還有留存
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父的想法 已經傳遞給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩形 活下去 和這份力量一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓不再使用你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 為了螢借給我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想傷害任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:13:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害了鳴人和詩形大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人和我都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背叛了詩形大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和禁術一起消失就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會看你這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟子就該聽師父的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父…的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧 螢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩形大人 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離我遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑我的力量 已經抑制不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 我會被撕裂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁術會爆發了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩形大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信師父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把這個村子徹底摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這一切都毀滅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多重影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難纏的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字縛之術.炎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你 我絕不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字縛之術.斬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點帶他去螢那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個讓人操心的弟子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁術如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好螢沒事 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土蜘蛛一族和木葉村約定的任務就全部完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是給大家添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁術雖然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣螢小姐也不會再被人盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村民也會同意接受螢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是打算和詩形一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有許多需要學習的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要接受師父的教導
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為能為土蜘蛛一族復興而出力的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 師父
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在開我的玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦 你終於肯做她的師傅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那螢就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 各位請保重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有師父果然是件好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有點想好色仙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是我第一次遇見師父的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢 可以在這裡稍等一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去見霧忍暗部的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要得到和你一起修行的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒有回復
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍他們出什麼意外了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六尾人柱力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們幹掉了劍他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要重建世界 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此你是必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是你體內的尾獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六尾我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢 你要活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.57,0:22:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倏地傳來了自來也的噩耗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.42,0:22:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這突如其來的消息 讓同伴們深受打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.42,0:22:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對這巨大的打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們手足無措 舉步維艱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻的木葉吹起了悲傷的暴風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.13,0:23:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影忍者疾風傳特別篇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人的眼淚 重振的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.75,0:23:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3月25日 週四晚7點 開始播放
